Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.40,0:00:07.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉好点了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.29,0:00:09.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是的 谢谢关心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.51,0:00:11.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.12,0:00:17.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御子乃在塔顶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.77,0:00:18.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.90,0:00:22.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通知各Element
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.98,0:00:26.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新九龙地区附近出现Abductor反应
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.32,0:00:28.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此训练中止
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.35,0:00:34.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪炎 婕希卡 安迪 以上三名同学请马上返回学校
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.42,0:00:38.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挚友 这里就交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.47,0:00:42.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你回学校去吧 山茶花 你也是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.61,0:00:44.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 御子乃现在身陷险境
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.03,0:00:49.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身为Element 比起任务你更倾向于妹妹吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.62,0:00:55.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.42,0:01:00.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真羡慕你们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.19,0:01:06.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比谁都更高更美的合体
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.14,0:01:10.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有我在的话 本该能实现的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,--------------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.10,0:01:15.30,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}畏れ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.60,0:01:19.48,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}living your life don't give up now keep moving on
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.67,0:01:24.88,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}君を抱き締める 何度も何度も何度も
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.34,0:01:30.52,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}明日僕は　君に出会うだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.72,0:01:36.68,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}わずかな星明りをたよりに
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.80,0:01:42.75,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}僕には君が分かるよ 分かるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.91,0:01:52.21,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}千億の時を越え 二人開く伝説の扉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.95,0:01:58.45,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}奈落の蒼飛び越えて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.48,0:02:04.42,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}君と灰になるため
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.45,0:02:15.34,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}長き輪でも 悲しみ連れて 旅してきたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.55,0:02:21.06,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}全力で未完成　君の隣で
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.28,0:02:27.03,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}乾いた心解け 血を流すけど
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.12,0:02:29.83,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}そばにいるよずっと
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.05,0:02:32.82,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}寄り添ってずっと
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.00,0:02:37.58,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}二人　光の船に乗る
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.60,0:02:43.25,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}風の始まりの音 奏でよう(目覚め)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.10,0:01:15.30,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}恐惧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.60,0:01:19.48,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}活出自己 永不放弃 继续前进
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.67,0:01:24.88,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}不论几次都想将你紧紧抱住
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.34,0:01:30.52,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}明天 我能和你相遇吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.72,0:01:36.68,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}就算仅靠那一点星光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.80,0:01:42.75,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}我也知道那是你 知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.91,0:01:52.21,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}两人越过千亿年的时光 打开传说之门
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.95,0:01:58.45,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}飞越地狱之空
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.48,0:02:04.42,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}一同化为尘埃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.45,0:02:15.34,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}在无尽的轮回中 也会带着悲伤的梦来旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.55,0:02:21.06,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}明明陪在你身边 用尽全力却也没有实现
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.28,0:02:27.03,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}解开冰冷的心 鲜血却一直流淌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.12,0:02:29.83,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}我将一直留在你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.05,0:02:32.82,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}一直紧跟着你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.00,0:02:37.58,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}当我们乘上光之船
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.60,0:02:43.25,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}那起风时的音符 将会奏响(觉醒吧)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,====================op
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.24,0:02:50.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.90,0:02:58.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好臭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.88,0:03:04.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但又臭中带甜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.55,0:03:08.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.67,0:03:10.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个反应是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.38,0:03:12.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是恋爱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.67,0:03:13.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.56,0:03:17.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,禁断的邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.09,0:03:22.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3}生命的亢奋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.29,0:03:27.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.35,0:03:36.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还真脆弱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.76,0:03:38.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快放开御子乃！！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.75,0:03:46.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的气味哪里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.87,0:03:50.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在你身上闻不到任何气味
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.18,0:03:53.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无臭无味的奇怪男人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.02,0:03:56.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.78,0:04:00.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以杀了你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.02,0:04:05.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不想被杀死
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.52,0:04:08.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.48,0:04:10.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 别走
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.04,0:04:13.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别妨碍我们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.64,0:04:17.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是只属于我的臭女人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.08,0:04:30.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 她不是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.83,0:04:37.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不会…我才不会把御子乃交给你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.51,0:04:43.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.31,0:05:09.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然长出了翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.74,0:05:18.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这声音是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.86,0:05:35.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神乐再度前往Vega
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.00,0:05:39.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是谁把门打开了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.26,0:05:43.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神乐的Guniss不是被严密地拘束着么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.74,0:05:47.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不见 出云
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.17,0:05:51.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jin也长大成人了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.32,0:05:55.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未影
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.67,0:05:57.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是你指使他的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.21,0:05:59.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是在什么时候醒来的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.16,0:06:01.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么时候?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.17,0:06:04.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是被吻醒的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.16,0:06:08.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被名为机械天使禁断之招的吻
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.60,0:06:10.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要帮助神乐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.16,0:06:13.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是从旁注视着而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.05,0:06:19.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目送着朝爱的新天地奔跑的被选中之人的背影
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.77,0:06:21.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱的新天地?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.00,0:06:25.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,释放禁断之招的机械天使
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.52,0:06:31.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其体内的RareIgler指引着神乐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.19,0:06:35.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能让他如此执迷的RareIgler
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.53,0:06:36.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道你就不感兴趣么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.22,0:06:45.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是足以操纵机械天使的RareIgler
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.71,0:06:50.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定能成为我们Altair真正的夏娃（Eve）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.40,0:06:58.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续监视Vega
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.92,0:07:03.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦他有异常举动 就强制收回Mithra Gunis
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.88,0:07:04.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.37,0:07:38.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾利西亚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.83,0:07:58.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以…杀掉你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.14,0:08:00.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么不可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.30,0:08:03.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你能将我演奏的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.27,0:08:17.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你身上也隐约散发着气味
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.76,0:08:20.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和那女人的气味很相似
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.08,0:08:27.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.05,0:08:42.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奏响的音色挺美妙的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.24,0:08:47.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修雷特留在了新九龙地区是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.49,0:08:48.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.72,0:08:51.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪炎 婕希卡 安迪 以上三名
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.68,0:08:53.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回来之后立即出击
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.32,0:08:53.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.01,0:08:59.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…我一直都感到很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.80,0:09:03.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么修雷特同学从不参加实战呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.28,0:09:11.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明他在模拟战中成绩名列前茅
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.62,0:09:13.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这到底是为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.20,0:09:14.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女生们不禁产生了疑问…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.65,0:09:16.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男女之间现在也没有隔阂了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.07,0:09:21.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们希望能了解今后可能会与之合体的Element的个人资料
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.84,0:09:34.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修雷特·艾兰自小就拥有惊人的音乐天赋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.08,0:09:40.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是他那钢琴曲的音色
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.68,0:09:43.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却蕴含着强烈的“负”的Element能力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.74,0:10:00.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能直接触及人类的深层心理
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.61,0:10:02.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修雷特的琴音会演绎出痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.24,0:10:04.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种谣言一传十 十传百
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.05,0:10:08.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最终 他成为了黑暗的工具
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.19,0:10:39.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这声音…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.19,0:10:59.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Neo Diva
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.16,0:11:07.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修雷特那家伙 是那个小孩子理事长找来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.34,0:11:10.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来 理事长有几岁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.23,0:11:12.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 在Element适应性检查过程中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.91,0:11:16.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们得知在修雷特身上有个严峻的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.54,0:11:20.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在乘坐Aquarion之时
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.74,0:11:23.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修雷特的生命会被削减
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.44,0:11:28.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Aquarion会放大Element的潜在力量
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.95,0:11:34.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同时将放大后的力量反馈到Element身上 从而相互强化
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.91,0:11:37.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修雷特的Element能力实在是过于强大
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.23,0:11:40.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在与Aquarion的力量接力中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.35,0:11:43.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他那虚弱的身体会不堪重负
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.78,0:11:45.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人从这里跳下去了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.97,0:11:50.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十分抱歉 琴稍微有点变形了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.63,0:11:54.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但仍旧能演奏出美妙的琴音
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.70,0:12:00.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我如痴如醉地死去的琴音
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.00,0:12:15.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御子乃同学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.33,0:12:19.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原谅…我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.92,0:12:27.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…必须…向那个人…道歉…才行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.34,0:12:28.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,道歉? 对那家伙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.69,0:12:31.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事 御子乃同学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.37,0:12:34.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Abductor警报
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.83,0:12:40.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Vector机
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.78,0:12:50.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个个都来妨碍我们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.21,0:12:53.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的臭女人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.22,0:12:56.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.20,0:13:22.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.36,0:13:27.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是那个像野兽一般的Abductor
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.62,0:13:28.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是Mithra Gunis
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.15,0:13:32.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是那台机体的名字吗 总司令
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.53,0:13:43.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐在这家伙里面 就更容易嗅出味道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.60,0:13:53.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪炎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.18,0:13:57.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.56,0:14:05.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是这架吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.41,0:14:08.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闪避开 婕希卡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.15,0:14:22.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.97,0:14:25.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙在找御子乃同学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.43,0:14:31.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御子乃同学 你醒来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.27,0:14:32.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿马塔…君？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.13,0:14:35.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.35,0:14:38.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御子乃同学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.88,0:14:41.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才 你说要向那家伙道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.70,0:14:43.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,道歉？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.59,0:14:46.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.31,0:14:51.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 被那人抓住的时候总觉得很害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.33,0:14:57.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 他对我那热情的举措
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.49,0:15:00.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得 有点熟悉…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.89,0:15:13.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 甩不掉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.48,0:15:35.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了 我的臭女人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.02,0:15:55.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事吧 挚友
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.31,0:15:57.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修雷特
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.72,0:16:04.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我来替代你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.20,0:16:07.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你的身体…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.91,0:16:21.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快把我的臭女人交出来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.97,0:16:23.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御子乃同学
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.58,0:16:25.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.68,0:16:28.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用管我了 阿马塔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.36,0:16:29.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.68,0:16:33.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也觉得那家伙似曾相识
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.40,0:16:40.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我下意识觉得唯独不能把你交给他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.98,0:16:48.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪炎?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.82,0:16:50.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不是 莫非是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.58,0:16:53.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修雷特
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.82,0:16:55.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么他会在Vector机内
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.07,0:17:02.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 这样你会…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.87,0:17:07.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个对手非同一般 这里只能由我来应战
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.92,0:17:10.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你的身体状况…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.37,0:17:11.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不动
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.82,0:17:12.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Element转换
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.22,0:17:15.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,换走安迪.W.霍尔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.23,0:17:19.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 亏我还以为今天终于可以跟女生合体…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.96,0:17:27.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臭女人 快过来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.71,0:17:31.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.41,0:17:33.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Vector Z
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.74,0:17:38.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御子乃同学你先逃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.61,0:17:41.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿马塔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.73,0:17:55.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克雷雅理事长 请下达合体许可
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.19,0:17:57.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修雷特 这万万不可
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.34,0:18:02.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不能演奏Aquarion 我死了也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.13,0:18:05.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这样的我虽生犹死
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.26,0:18:25.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我许可你们合体
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.10,0:18:29.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修雷特?艾兰 你就是头部
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.65,0:18:39.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我演奏Aquarion的时刻终于到来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.53,0:18:44.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,旋律合体 Go Aquarion
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.53,0:18:59.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剧烈的轰鸣 响彻心底
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.29,0:19:02.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 却让人格外怀念
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.28,0:19:05.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是生命之音
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.95,0:19:08.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是纯真的赤子呱呱坠地时的第一声啼哭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.03,0:19:16.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Aquarion SPADA
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.59,0:19:19.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以Vector Y为头部的合体
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.41,0:19:21.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Aquarion SPADA
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.41,0:19:21.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs25}SPADA：在意大利语里是“剑”的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.06,0:19:30.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修雷特的力量衍生出新的力量形态
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.99,0:19:38.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Aquarion
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.05,0:19:46.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自从第一次看到你 我体内那颗死寂的心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.52,0:19:49.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随即奏响了热情洋溢的心跳断奏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.29,0:19:52.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 那就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.09,0:19:54.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灵魂的旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.50,0:20:01.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶的机械天使 我不会再让你妨碍我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.11,0:20:03.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿马塔 婕希卡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.52,0:20:07.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所谓的生存 就是削减生命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.55,0:20:10.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其体现在演奏生命和豁出生命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.23,0:20:15.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,借我力量 让我演奏生命吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.36,0:20:16.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.40,0:20:18.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不能对那家伙坐视不理
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.31,0:20:24.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.53,0:20:26.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灵魂的琶音
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.92,0:20:34.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.06,0:20:40.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿马塔的Element能力——飞翔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.13,0:20:43.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后还有婕希卡的冲击
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.76,0:20:47.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两者与修雷德的力量合为一体之时
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.69,0:20:52.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若伴有天之月的颤音和水之月的活泼快板
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.78,0:20:53.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.95,0:20:58.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人之月就会热情地讴歌生命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.50,0:21:01.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,月下葬送曲（MOONLIGHT REQUIEM）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.99,0:21:07.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.75,0:21:31.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成…成功了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.90,0:21:38.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没结束 我还能战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.95,0:21:44.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 我要回收Mithra Gunis
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.92,0:21:47.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你别在调查Vega的过程中鲁莽行事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.08,0:21:49.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这会增加我的工作负担
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.97,0:21:52.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jin 你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.52,0:21:58.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙想逃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.18,0:22:01.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修雷特 赶紧乘胜追击
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.27,0:22:04.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修雷特
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.67,0:22:06.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下 修雷特他…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.52,0:22:10.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修雷特 你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.16,0:22:11.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修雷特
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.05,0:22:12.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修雷特
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.24,0:22:20.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.75,0:22:23.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御子乃 你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.21,0:22:26.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道 我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.98,0:22:32.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不知道 但我却感到很难过
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.44,0:24:15.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你听说过关于消失了的Element的怪谈吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.96,0:24:18.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不妙啊 这太可怕啊 晚上连上厕所都不敢了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.04,0:24:21.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为以防万一 要先挖个洞吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.86,0:24:24.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下回 Aquarion EVOL
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.24,0:24:25.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深夜中的少女
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,====================================
